## TECH STACK (LOCKED — DO NOT CHANGE)
- Framework: Next.js 15 App Router + TypeScript
- UI: shadcn/ui components + Tailwind CSS
- Auth + DB + Storage: Supabase (@supabase/ssr)
- PDF Stamping: pdf-lib (CLIENT-SIDE ONLY — no server needed)
- PDF Generation: @react-pdf/renderer
- Word Templates: docxtemplater + pizzip
- Email: Resend
- Deployment: Vercel (serverless)
- Automation: n8n (external, self-hosted)
- Telegram: Telegram Bot API (via n8n)
- LLM: DeepSeek V4 Flash ONLY — model: "deepseek-chat"
  Endpoint: https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions
  NO OTHER LLM PROVIDERS — this is final and locked

